Eduction.title: Agile Full stack Web Developer
duties: codeX is a full time, one year coding program in Cape Town that trains and places bright young talent as software developers.
At codeX you learn practical skills the tech industry demands and we help you find a job at a top local company that suits your interests and ambitions.

codeX aims to solve two of Africas major challenges: youth unemployment and a critical programming skills gap. We find, train, and place young developer talent in great entry-level jobs and ensure they have the solid foundation they need to build long-term digital careers.
